        public void drive()
        Allows the drivers to drive the robot with G1 left and right joysticks. Also lets drivers automatically align the robot to face one of the alliance goals. G1 left, right joystick - drivetrain control G1 B button - align robot to face to red goal G1 X button - align robot to face blue goal
